==English==

=== Etymology ===
[[macro-]] and [[region]]

=== Noun ===
#A administrative system that is equivalent to a [[prefecture]] or a [[department]].  It is used in [[Brazil]] as a third-level administration between [[state]] and [[micro-region]].

